or: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;"><br></span></strong></em></span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">为认真贯彻落实市委、市政府和园区党工委、管委会关于整治火灾隐患的工作要求，阳澄湖半岛旅游度假区党工委强化组织领导，加强隐患排查，成立“企业管家”行动支部，全面开展“431”专项行动。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><br></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.6195652173913043" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvmEmsnBTbN1Bo3dlpj7F5tWiajuuXVFciaAicLrxh6sJVMCdI4l3TrqtVWuoxSW1ZYzJ2GN8yc4fGd7A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="920" style="box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 14px 0px;"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">阳澄湖半岛旅游度假区党工委成立“企业管家”行动支部</span></strong><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">，根据现有网格，由行动支部党员担任网格长、安监网格员协同，围绕企业“三合一”、电动自行车等火灾隐患迅速响应，对辖区企业和大型商贸体的火灾隐患开展地毯式全面排查。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br></p><section class="_editor" style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;white-space: normal;"><section><section><section><section class="_editor"><section><section><section><section class="_editor"><section style="margin: 7px 5.57813px 20px;text-align: center;"><section style="height: 2em;display: inline-block;"><section style="padding-right: 0.3em;padding-left: 0.3em;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;height: 2em;line-height: 2em;border-top: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 72, 58);border-bottom: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 72, 58);border-left: 0.1em solid rgb(239